ca.ualberta.cmput301f14t16.easya.Model

Class Pending

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f14t16.easya.Model.Pending

  • public class Pending
extends java.lang.Object
    Pending is cache like buffer used to store a Question, Answer or Reply object that has not yet been submitted. Once the device acquires an Internet connection, Any stored data is pushed to the webservice, and Pending is cleared of data. A Pending object will store all parents of the stored Content.
    Version:
    1.1 Build 1000 Oct 27st, 2014.
    Author:
    Lingbo Tang, Cauani
